      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">32.106</ph> Order of preference.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The contracting officer must consider the following order of preference when a contractor requests contract financing, unless an exception would be in the Governmentâ€™s best interest in a specific case:</p>
         <ol id="d2022e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2047e12" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Private financing without Government guarantee. It is not intended, however, that the contracting officer require the contractor to obtain private financing-</p>
               <ol id="d2022e26" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2047e18" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                At unreasonable terms; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2047e23" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                From other agencies.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2047e28" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Customary contract financing other than loan guarantees and certain advance payments (see <xref href="32.113.dita#FAR_32_113"
                        base="i1083846"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.113</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2047e36" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            Loan guarantees.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2047e41" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
						            Unusual contract financing (see <xref href="32.114.dita#FAR_32_114"
                        base="i1083893"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.114</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2047e49" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
						            Advance payments (see exceptions in <xref href="32.402.dita#FAR_32_402"
                        base="i1082582"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.402</xref>(b)).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
